What are you thinking? Huh?

277
00:17:47,025 --> 00:17:48,026
We're not doing this.

278
00:17:48,569 --> 00:17:49,570
'Kay?

279
00:17:50,362 --> 00:17:53,657
You're giving him half the gold.
Buying a ferry ticket.

280
00:17:54,074 --> 00:17:55,659
You can't think like that anymore.

281
00:17:56,743 --> 00:17:58,579
We have to start looking out
for ourselves first.

282
00:18:14,303 --> 00:18:19,600
JG JANGGAK TRADE INC.
TRADING/ TRANSPORT/ LOGISTICS

283
00:18:29,526 --> 00:18:30,527
Heeju.

284
00:18:37,075 --> 00:18:38,243
The gold bars.

285
00:18:39,328 --> 00:18:40,537
Why don't you just tell me where they are?

286
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:43,290
It'd be just in case.

287
00:18:43,373 --> 00:18:46,502
If anything bad were to happen to you,
then don't you think I should know?

288
00:18:46,585 --> 00:18:47,878
Woogy.

289
00:18:47,961 --> 00:18:48,962
Why don't we do this?

290
00:18:49,755 --> 00:18:51,173
You could schedule an E-mail.

291
00:18:51,256 --> 00:18:53,342
Write it in there,
set it to send later.

292
00:18:53,425 --> 00:18:55,719
And if you come back safely,
you could just delete it.

293
00:18:57,179 --> 00:18:59,181
So then if I were to come back safely...

294
00:19:00,098 --> 00:19:01,475
...you would just kill me, right?

295
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:05,062
Right, I see why you'd think that.

296
00:19:06,855 --> 00:19:08,398
Heeju, just be careful.

297
00:19:08,482 --> 00:19:10,025
-I really mean it, okay?
-Okay.

298
00:19:10,108 --> 00:19:12,569
Seriously, those guys can be crazy.
You need to watch your back.

299
00:19:27,334 --> 00:19:28,335
Kim Heeju?

300
00:19:35,217 --> 00:19:36,260
What is this?

301
00:19:38,011 --> 00:19:39,012
Anywhere?

302
00:19:41,056 --> 00:19:42,057
