303
00:19:44,351 --> 00:19:48,021
There's a ferry leaving Mokcheon Port
in two days, if that works for you.

304
00:19:48,105 --> 00:19:49,648
What are you loading?

305
00:19:49,731 --> 00:19:51,233
There's one car.

306
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:53,360
And one passenger.

307
00:19:53,443 --> 00:19:54,736
