I'll give you another one.

313
00:20:29,563 --> 00:20:32,900
All right, Park, you asshole.
Just show up already.

314
00:20:42,159 --> 00:20:43,327
Hey, yeah, Chief Cheon.

315
00:20:43,410 --> 00:20:45,078
Park is here right now.
You coming or what?

316
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:48,874
Is that Park?

317
00:20:52,878 --> 00:20:54,838
HEEJU, DIRECTOR PARK IS HERE.

318
00:20:59,927 --> 00:21:01,345
GET OUT OF THERE RIGHT NOW.

319
00:21:02,429 --> 00:21:03,472
What?

320
00:21:07,559 --> 00:21:11,480
Wait. Did you mess around
with Geumseong's stuff?

321
00:21:11,563 --> 00:21:15,943
You did! Come here! Come over here!
Quickly! Go, go, go, go, go!

322
00:21:16,026 --> 00:21:17,611
Hide here!

323
00:21:18,695 --> 00:21:21,698
In here! Okay. Inside this!
You need to get in. Okay.

324
00:21:21,782 --> 00:21:25,410
They won't find you in here. Here!
Don't even breathe! Okay?

325
00:21:25,494 --> 00:21:28,247
Don't make any noise!
You need to stay hidden in here!

326
00:21:28,330 --> 00:21:30,582
Okay, good. Good.

327
00:21:33,836 --> 00:21:35,879
Oh, fuck me!

328
00:21:36,964 --> 00:21:38,715
Oh, gosh, I don't know!

329
00:21:38,799 --> 00:21:39,967
Ah!

330
00:21:41,176 --> 00:21:43,512
Hey there, Donggu.
It's been a while.

331
00:21:46,849 --> 00:21:50,227
Hey, I think there was a misunderstanding,
right?

332
00:21:51,228 --> 00:21:52,145
What?

333
00:21:57,734 --> 00:21:59,319
You know I don't say things I don't mean.

334
00:21:59,403 --> 00:22:01,530
Where'd you hide the casket?

335
00:22:02,072 --> 00:22:04,032
Tell me or I'll take your other ear.

336
00:22:04,116 --> 00:22:05,492
This is all a misunderstanding!

337
00:22:05,576 --> 00:22:08,620
This isn't a funeral home!
Why would you look for a casket here?

338
00:22:08,704 --> 00:22:10,289
Wait!

339
00:22:16,044 --> 00:22:17,087
Stop it!

340
00:22:26,555 --> 00:22:28,473
What the actual fuck?

341
00:22:28,557 --> 00:22:29,558
Get up there!

342
00:22:39,234 --> 00:22:42,863
Ju! Ju Haran! Ah!
It's Ju Haran!

343
00:22:42,946 --> 00:22:44,323
It's Ju Haran!

344
00:22:44,406 --> 00:22:46,074
Who is Ju Haran?

345
00:22:51,997 --> 00:22:53,123
Oh, shit!

346
00:22:53,207 --> 00:22:55,250
Hey, boss!

347
00:22:55,334 --> 00:22:56,668
- Hurry!
- Fuck's sake!

348
00:22:56,752 --> 00:22:57,794
Ju Haran!
Who the fuck is she?

349
00:22:57,878 --> 00:22:59,129
