368
00:23:46,009 --> 00:23:47,636
- He's the one who stole the casket.
- Bullshit!

369
00:23:47,719 --> 00:23:49,847
-He took it.
-I don't fucking have it, you liar!

370
00:23:50,597 --> 00:23:52,850
Just, fuck.

371
00:23:52,933 --> 00:23:54,643
Just give me a second to explain!

372
00:23:54,726 --> 00:23:56,019
