374
00:23:59,314 --> 00:24:01,066
- Ju Haran, huh?
- Fuck, how many times

375
00:24:01,149 --> 00:24:03,318
do I have to tell you?
How do I explain this?

376
00:24:03,402 --> 00:24:05,571
I have no idea, really!
I don't know!

377
00:24:05,654 --> 00:24:07,322
