388
00:24:50,991 --> 00:24:53,243
Come and get it, you motherfucker.

389
00:24:53,327 --> 00:24:56,747
Wow. You're fucking stubborn.

390
00:24:58,123 --> 00:24:59,416
Keep him alive, okay?

391
00:25:01,126 --> 00:25:02,753
Wait!

392
00:26:01,687 --> 00:26:02,980
You fucking asshole!

393
00:26:09,152 --> 00:26:10,737
Oh, fuck.

394
00:26:32,301 --> 00:26:33,635
Wait, wait, wait!

395
00:26:34,386 --> 00:26:37,931
Okay, okay! You win, Park!
You win, Park! You win, Park, okay?

396
00:26:38,015 --> 00:26:40,058
Just a sec.
Let's not do this.

397
00:26:40,142 --> 00:26:41,894
We'll let you go if you just apologize.

398
00:26:41,977 --> 00:26:43,520
We can just bring
any old document and-

399
00:26:43,604 --> 00:26:46,773
Shit, okay, never mind! I'm sorry, okay?

400
00:26:46,857 --> 00:26:48,442
Let's just find the casket!

401
00:26:48,525 --> 00:26:50,819
Then the Chairman'll spare your life,
