402
00:26:51,361 --> 00:26:52,946
I can explain everything.

403
00:26:54,865 --> 00:26:55,908
Boss!

404
00:26:55,991 --> 00:26:57,409
Have you lost your mind?

405
00:26:59,328 --> 00:27:01,663
Shit. Fuck!

406
00:27:08,045 --> 00:27:10,088
You wanna save him,
you better take him to the hospital.

407
00:27:15,427 --> 00:27:16,720
Boss!

408
00:27:16,803 --> 00:27:18,222
Oh, man.

409
00:27:20,807 --> 00:27:22,726
What the-
is Park running away?

410
00:27:22,809 --> 00:27:25,187
Shit. Shit.

411
00:27:25,729 --> 00:27:27,022
This fucking...

412
00:27:41,787 --> 00:27:43,121
Oh, sh-

413
00:27:51,755 --> 00:27:54,258
What the fuck is even going on?

414
00:27:54,341 --> 00:27:57,302
Hey, what happened here?
Heo Donggu, what just happened?

415
00:27:57,386 --> 00:27:58,554
Oh, fuck!

416
00:27:58,637 --> 00:28:01,014
What do you think happened?
Just take a look around!

417
00:28:01,098 --> 00:28:03,225
Ju Haran, I'm looking for her.
Have you seen her?

418
00:28:03,308 --> 00:28:06,061
Ju Haran? Well, I dunno.
Look at this place. I dunno.

419
00:28:06,144 --> 00:28:08,689
I saw her walk in here with my own eyes,
you asshole!

420
00:28:08,772 --> 00:28:10,649
What are you talking about?
Nobody came here!

421
00:28:10,732 --> 00:28:12,150
Can't you see this mess?

422
00:28:12,234 --> 00:28:14,319
You motherfucker! If you're lying to me,
I swear I'll fucking kill you.

423
00:28:14,403 --> 00:28:16,822
I'm not lying! Why would I?
I'm not lying to you! I swear!

424
00:28:16,905 --> 00:28:17,906
Detective Kim!

425
00:28:17,990 --> 00:28:19,283
Over here!

426
00:28:19,825 --> 00:28:21,076
Help me out!

427
00:28:21,159 --> 00:28:22,744
- Please, hurry!
- This fucking...

428
00:28:22,828 --> 00:28:24,913
Detective Kim!
Come on, hurry up!

429
00:28:24,997 --> 00:28:27,499
-Get over here! Come on, hurry!
-What happened to Chief Cheon?

430
00:28:27,583 --> 00:28:28,792
Come on, get over here!

431
00:28:30,961 --> 00:28:32,212
Here we go.

432
00:28:33,046 --> 00:28:34,965
Get him out of here.

433
00:28:35,048 --> 00:28:36,216
-Stay with us, Chief Cheon!
-Shit.

434
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:39,344
If you die, we'll all end up dead!
Come on, we gotta move!

435
00:28:42,931 --> 00:28:44,892
Come on!

436
00:28:45,767 --> 00:28:47,144
Shit.

437
00:28:47,227 --> 00:28:48,812
Oh!

438
00:28:49,229 --> 00:28:50,272
Hello? Heeju?

439
00:28:50,814 --> 00:28:52,399
Tell me what the fuck
is goin' on in there!

440
00:28:52,482 --> 00:28:54,234
Woogy, you have to run.

441
00:28:54,318 --> 00:28:56,236
Detective Kim is heading your way.

442
00:28:56,945 --> 00:28:58,197
What are you gonna-

443
00:28:58,280 --> 00:28:59,281
Hello?

444
00:29:00,282 --> 00:29:01,283
Shit.

445
00:29:01,366 --> 00:29:04,077
Chief Cheon!
Please, please, don't die!

446
00:29:04,745 --> 00:29:06,788
Please don't die!

447
00:29:06,872 --> 00:29:08,582
We're in big trouble.

448
00:29:11,668 --> 00:29:13,003
No!

449
00:29:13,795 --> 00:29:14,922
They're all gone.

450
00:29:18,926 --> 00:29:20,511
You can come out now.

451
00:29:32,189 --> 00:29:33,190
Listen.

452
00:29:33,774 --> 00:29:34,942
Let's make a deal.

453
00:29:36,568 --> 00:29:38,820
Those men,
the ones that were here,

454
00:29:38,904 --> 00:29:40,280
I'm not like them at all.

455
00:29:41,114 --> 00:29:42,783
And I'm not that greedy, either.

456
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:46,203
I'm not ambitious.

457
00:29:46,286 --> 00:29:48,664
All I'd like is to live a long life.

458
00:29:49,414 --> 00:29:53,460
And drugs, I'm out of that business.
I cut all connections ten years ago!

459
00:29:53,544 --> 00:29:54,920
I'm my own man now.

460
00:29:55,754 --> 00:29:57,005
The casket...

461
00:29:58,257 --> 00:30:01,218
Listen, shit, I really don't care
about it at all.

462
00:30:02,135 --> 00:30:04,429
Why else would I hide you in that cabinet?

463
00:30:04,513 --> 00:30:07,975
I hid you and I didn't tell those guys
that you're actually Kim Heeju,

464
00:30:08,058 --> 00:30:09,309
not Ju Haran.

465
00:30:11,812 --> 00:30:13,230
So what do you want from me?

466
00:30:15,732 --> 00:30:17,067
The transport fee.

467
00:30:18,277 --> 00:30:19,570
Ten gold bars.

468
00:30:20,237 --> 00:30:21,363
One billion won?

469
00:30:23,323 --> 00:30:24,992
We can negotiate, too.

470
00:30:25,075 --> 00:30:27,911
And also, uh,
after sales service?

471
00:30:27,995 --> 00:30:30,372
I'll take full responsibility
for everything right up till the end!

472
00:30:30,455 --> 00:30:31,456
I swear it!

473
00:30:33,208 --> 00:30:34,376
I mean it.

474
00:30:36,628 --> 00:30:39,339
Look, that car over there.

475
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:42,843
It's collateral I got yesterday.
You can take it. It's on me.

476
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:45,262
I haven't even taken it to the garage yet.

477
00:30:45,345 --> 00:30:48,849
Feel free to drive it as much as you want,
and then get rid of it.

478
00:31:02,654 --> 00:31:04,198
You can rest now.

479
00:31:09,995 --> 00:31:12,581
No need to make a big deal out of it.
Just have him cremated.

480
00:31:12,664 --> 00:31:13,665
Yes, sir.

481
00:31:14,208 --> 00:31:16,668
-Let Kim Jinman take care of the rest.
-Yes, sir.

482
00:31:17,085 --> 00:31:18,587
Have you found Park Hocheol yet?

483
00:31:19,546 --> 00:31:20,672
No.

484
00:31:20,756 --> 00:31:21,757
What?

485
00:31:23,175 --> 00:31:26,094
Get out there and find him immediately
before I rip each and every one of you

486
00:31:26,178 --> 00:31:27,513
-into fucking pieces!
-Right away.

487
00:31:36,313 --> 00:31:37,940
Are you doing okay, Ko?

488
00:31:38,607 --> 00:31:39,775
Yes, I'm okay, sir.

489
00:31:41,318 --> 00:31:43,570
Did you really not know
that Park had a lead?

490
00:31:44,488 --> 00:31:46,073
On the casket?

491
00:31:46,573 --> 00:31:50,327
Well, I hadn't really considered
that he would still be after it, sir.

492
00:31:50,410 --> 00:31:54,623
Honestly, uh,
I thought he'd gone back to Yes Money

493
00:31:54,706 --> 00:31:56,625
-and just given up on it.
-Whatever.

494
00:31:56,708 --> 00:31:59,169
Now bring me either Lee Dokyung
or Ju Haran.

495
00:31:59,253 --> 00:32:02,631
You're supposed to be the expert on this.
Just do your job.

496
00:32:02,714 --> 00:32:04,550
Then I'll get 'em to talk.

497
00:32:05,342 --> 00:32:06,969
Let's stick to what we're good at.

498
00:32:07,761 --> 00:32:08,762
Yes, sir.

499
00:32:09,346 --> 00:32:13,183
But if Park Hocheol finds that girl
or the casket before you do...

500
00:32:14,309 --> 00:32:16,645
